xDirections.title: To add breakdown: double click Color/Print cell.To delete: hold down Command key (Mac) or Control key (Windows) and double click Color/Print cell.

Text2.title: Shift & double click anywhere but Customer or Note to delete. Click note to expand.

Text.title: To avoid confusion, the total number of garments entered in the size breakdown must equal the number of units in the order.If you do not know the full breakdown, click the clear button and reset the breakdown. Reenter when information is complete.

Text26.title: Vu = Display EM = Email BL = Blank Line

Text5.title: Double click to remove. Drag and drop to reorder.
